title: Draft WeekPalooza Day 3- Sandwich Props & Sessler Mock Draft
itunes:title: Draft WeekPalooza Day 3- Sandwich Props & Sessler Mock Draft
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you the draftiest of all draft shows kicking off with some draft related sandwich props (5:45). Marc Sessler reveals his highly anticipated mock draft (33:35) and Spicerack joins the show to talk about some draft prospects (56:52). It's chaotic, we love it.
